#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

string add (string &s1, string &s2)
{
	int carry=0,sum,i;
	string  min=s1,max=s2,result = "";
	if (s1.length()>s2.length())
	{
		max = s1;
		min = s2;
	}
	else
	{
		max = s2;
		min = s1;
	}
	for (i = min.length()-1; i>=0; i--)
	{
		sum = min[i] + max[i + max.length() - min.length()] + carry - 2*'0';
		carry = sum/10;
		sum %=10;
		result = (char)(sum + '0') + result;
	}
	i = max.length() - min.length()-1;
	while (i>=0)
	{
		sum = max[i] + carry - '0';
		carry = sum/10;
		sum%=10;
		result = (char)(sum + '0') + result;
		i--;
	}
	if (carry!=0)
	{
		result = (char)(carry + '0') + result;
	}
	return result;
}
int main ()
{
	string a,b;
	cin >> a >> b;
	cout << "Result = ";
	cout << add (a,b) << endl;
	return 0;
}
